title: Game Night & Holiday Party
desc: Spades, Connect Four, Twister, Taboo, Bid Wist... do you have game? Join in on the fun and games from 5-8pm, then hang out with us to spread some holiday cheer from 8pm-12am at Brooklyn Alumnae's Game Night and Holiday Party. Tickets are $16 -- available from a Brooklyn Alumnae Delta or via Eventbrite. No monies at the door will be collected after 9pm. Note that the venue is   but an ATM is present on the premises.
